Package io.github.ai4ci.util

Annotation Type Factor.Level

Enclosing interface:
Factor
@Inherited @Target(FIELD) @Retention(RUNTIME) public static @interface Factor.Level
Annotation for specifying a custom label for an enum constant.

When applied to an enum constant, the value of this annotation is used as the label for that constant. If not present, the enum name is used as the label by default.
